11. Simple Dockerfile
FROM node:18
WORKDIR /app
COPY . .
RUN npm install
CMD ["npm", "start"]
Explanation:

FROM → base image
WORKDIR → set path
COPY → copy code
RUN → install deps
CMD → start app

